title: Animal Physiology Laboratory
description: Experiments conducted with primary focus on quantitative physiological principles of organ systems and intact organisms. Students cannot receive credit for this course and BIOL 130L.

pre_req_data.text: Prerequisite(s): BIOL 20A, BIOE 20B, and BIOE 20C. Concurrent enrollment in BIOE 131 is required.

class_notes: Concurrent enrollment in BIOE 131 is required.
